solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public boolean isUgly(int num) {--newline--        if(num==1) return true;--newline--        if(num==0) return false;--newline--        while(num%2==0) num=num>>1;--newline--        while(num%3==0) num=num/3;--newline--        while(num%5==0) num=num/5;--newline--        return num==1;--newline--    }--newline--}
